                input#chapterEmail.form-control(placeholder='', name='', type='text')
        .modal-footer
          button.btn.btn-default(data-event-title='chapter-cancel', data-dismiss='modal', type='button') Cancel
          button#login-button.btn.btn-default.red(data-event-title='submit', type='button') Submit
  // END Login
  // END Chapter
  // Main Panel
  .area-content
    .container
      .row.bottom-margin(style='margin-bottom: 10px;')
        h1.text-center College Cryptocurrency Network.
      .row
        p.description.f24.text-center
          | Named after the “original” cryptocurrency, “Bitcoin Clubs” have proliferated at many of the world’s most prestigious colleges and universities since 2012. Independent of one another, these clubs have been great successes, fostering dialogue and drawing in acclaimed guest speakers. In their short time in existence, College Bitcoiners have gone on to create successful cryptocurrency startups and have received considerable coverage by the press.
          | Recognizing the inherent strength in numbers, the College Cryptocurrency Network has brought these groups together to form a strong, collective entity.
          | Learn about the success and activities of existing chapters and the tools you can use to start a College Cryptocurrency club at your college or university today. CCN is here to help!
        // <img src="img/logo.png" alt="slide_7" class="img100 p40 animated bounceInUp" />
        .clearfix
        // Donate button
        .pull-right
          a.btn-default.green.getStartedNow.mr140(data-toggle='modal', href='#contactModal') Form A Chapter
        .clearfix
  // END Main Panel
  // Mission Panel
  .area-content
    .container.pb0
      .row.bottom-margin
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12
          h2.text-center.f45 Our Mission
      .iconed-features.lift-on-hover.style-1
        .row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-4
            .iconed-feature
              .feature-icon-w
                i.fa.fa-globe
              h4 Robust Networks
              p
                | The College Cryptocurrency Network (CCN) is an international nonprofit organization dedicated to forming a robust network of college clubs for cryptocurrency education, mining, trading, and start-ups.
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-4
            .iconed-feature
              .feature-icon-w
                i.fa.fa-btc
              h4 Innovations
              p
                | The CCN was established to help nascent, burgeoning, and not-yet existing college organizations build a presence on their respective campuses, receive administrative recognition and funding, and to help students connect with similar college groups.
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-4
            .iconed-feature
              .feature-icon-w
                i.fa.fa-briefcase
              h4 Resources
              p
                | We provide educational and professional resources, contacts, speakers, and guidance in order to usher in a new era of electronic finance and innovation.
